{"tid":2299352,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"疑．媽 RUN 討論區","createTime":"2020-11-24T16:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T14:30:08.000Z","uid":86269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"158552cbe3196785e406833c70359e7a5f9ae163","tid":2299352,"uid":86269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"疑．媽<br />\nRun<br />\n<img src=\"https://movie.yahoo-leisure.hk/assets/poster/b7dbe57d95e2f22c50126dd8a13c0384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.yahoo-leisure.hk%2Fassets%2Fposter%2Fb7dbe57d95e2f22c50126dd8a13c0384.jpg&h=5663564a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n高怡（姬拉艾倫 飾） 自幼體弱多病兼且雙腿不良於行，因此自出生起，就過著與世隔絕的生活；從衣、食、住、行，以至教育，都由母親戴安（莎拉寶森 飾）獨力一手包辦。隨著年齡漸長，高怡開始厭倦被母全面操控的生活；更甚的是，她無意中竟發現，一直以來無微不至的照顧，不是單純出於母愛，而是包含著連串令她冷汗直流的暗黑秘密&hellip;"},{"pid":"80797a9fcaf3b7b6689af90c55d7ad87579a6b26","tid":2299352,"uid":17031,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"我知我咁講好仆街<br />\n但係我係youtube見到有大陸人做依套電影嘅解說<br />\n然後我忍唔住睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa181e12c8a1634ddd3bd74c29a0d6b7cef3dfe","tid":2299352,"uid":86269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"劇透<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fddbf1b53fb035c66d58fddb92379bcefc989a5","tid":2299352,"uid":66893,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"80797a9fcaf3b7b6689af90c55d7ad87579a6b26","tid":2299352,"uid":17031,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"我知我咁講好仆街<br />\n但係我係youtube見到有大陸人做依套電影嘅解說<br />\n然後我忍唔住睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"Hulu上左架啦，你話你上網down左黎睇，都最多話你唔尊重知識產權。而家你睇埋d 19雞精片，到頭來你冇睇過套戲，但你又覺得自己睇左，唔會真係睇返套戲一次，咁有咩意思呀。大陸人都識睇左套戲先做解說啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 